目前 菲謝爾 存在bug。
Russian:
Отключить время зарядки лука.
Известны проблемы с Фишль.

SimplifiedChinese: 关闭玩家动画。允许空中释放技能

column1:
Distance between the player and the loot.
Values under 1.5 may be too intruding.
English:
Distance between the player and the loot.
Values under 1.5 may be too intruding.
SimplifiedChinese:
玩家与物品间的距离。
范围低于1.5m也许会有所影响。
TraditionalChinese:
玩家與物品間的距離。
範圍低於1.5m也許會有所影響。
Russian:
Дистанция между пероснажем и предметом.
Значения ниже 1.5 может быть слишком навязчивым.

column1: Distance between the player and the monster.
English: Distance between the player and the monster.

column1:
Do fix positions to nearest to point.
Only items with green line support this function.
English:
Do fix positions to nearest to point.
Only items with green line support this function.
SimplifiedChinese:
将位置固定到离点最近的位置。
只有带绿线的项目支持此功能。
TraditionalChinese:
將位置固定到離點最近的位置。
只有帶綠線的項目支持此功能。
Russian:
Do fix positions to nearest to point.
Only items with green line support this function.

column1: Draw tracer from middle part of the screen.
English: Draw tracer from middle part of the screen.
SimplifiedChinese: 从屏幕的中间部分开始绘制追踪线
TraditionalChinese: 從螢幕的中間部分開始繪制追蹤線

SimplifiedChinese:
穿着纹理。
示例路径: C:\Dress.png
TraditionalChinese:
穿著材質。
範例路徑: C:\Dress.png

column1:
Elemental sight is kept on even when moving.
To turn off, toggle off and use Elemental Sight again.
English:
Elemental sight is kept on even when moving.
To turn off, toggle off and use Elemental Sight again.
SimplifiedChinese:
永久启用元素视野。
如想要关闭，关闭此选项并使用一次元素视野。
TraditionalChinese:
永久啟用元素視野。
如想要關閉，關閉此選項並使用一次元素視野。
Russian:
Чувство стихий сохранятеся даже при движении.
Чтобы отключить, выключите функцию и снова используйте Чувство стихий.

column1: Enable automatic forward teleporation between teleports
English: Enable automatic forward teleporation between teleports
SimplifiedChinese: 启用后，自动传送下一个点位。
TraditionalChinese: 啟用後，自動傳送下一個點位。
Russian: Enable automatic forward teleporation between teleports

column1: Enable blocking and modifying packets by sniffer, can cause network lags.
English: Enable blocking and modifying packets by sniffer, can cause network lags.
SimplifiedChinese: 启动 抓包阻塞和修改数据包，可能会导致网络延迟。
TraditionalChinese: 啟動 抓包阻塞和修改封包，可能會導致網絡延遲。
Russian: Включить блокировку и изменение пакетов с помощью сниффера, может привести к задержкам в сети.

column1: Enable capturing of packet info and sending to pipe, if it exists.
English: Enable capturing of packet info and sending to pipe, if it exists.
SimplifiedChinese: 启用 捕获数据包信息并发送到管道(如果存在)
TraditionalChinese: 啟用 捕獲封包信息並發送到管道(如果存在)
Russian: Включить захват информации о пакете и отправку по каналу, если он существует.

SimplifiedChinese: 启用 宝箱检测和过滤器
TraditionalChinese: 啟用 寶箱檢測和過濾器

column1: Enable console for logging information (changes will take effect after relaunch)
English: Enable console for logging information (changes will take effect after relaunch)
SimplifiedChinese: 启用控制台以记录信息(更改将在游戏重新启动后生效)
TraditionalChinese: 啟用控制台以記錄信息(更改將在遊戲重新啟動後生效)
Russian: Enable console for logging information (changes will take effect after relaunch)

column1:
Enable custom pickup range.
High values are not recommended, as it is easily detected by the server.

If using with auto-pickup/auto-treasure, turn this on LAST.
English:
Enable custom pickup range.
High values are not recommended, as it is easily detected by the server.

If using with auto-pickup/auto-treasure, turn this on LAST.
SimplifiedChinese:
启动范围拾取，拾取范围的数值不建议过高，因为它很容易被服务器检测到。

如果要与自动拾取/自动宝藏一起使用，请确保最后打开该选项。
TraditionalChinese:
啟動範圍拾取，拾取範圍的數值不建議過高，因為它很容易被伺服器檢測到。

如果要與自動拾取/自動寶藏一起使用，請確保最後打開該選項。
Russian:
Включить настраиваемый диапазон подбора.
Высокие значения не рекомендуются, посколько это легко обнаруживается сервером.

При использовании с автоподбором/авто-сундуками, включите это в ПОСЛЕДНЮЮ очередь.

column1:
Enable delay fluctuation.
Simulates human clicking delay as manual clickling never consistent.
English:
Enable delay fluctuation.
Simulates human clicking delay as manual clickling never consistent.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用随机延迟。
模拟人类点击延迟，因为手动拾取间隔永远不会相同。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用隨機延遲。
模擬人類點擊延遲，因為手動拾取間隔永遠不會相同。
Russian:
Включить варьируемую задержку.
Имитирует человеческую задержку нажатия, посколько ручное нажатие никогда не бывает последовательным.

column1:
Enable detection of unknown items.
You can see these items below, if they exist.
English:
Enable detection of unknown items.
You can see these items below, if they exist.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用对未知道具的检测。
你可以在下面看到这些道具(如果存在)。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用對未知道具的檢測。
你可以在下面看到這些道具(如果存在)。
Russian:
Enable detection of unknown items.
You can see these items below, if they exist.

column1:
Enable file logging (changes will take effect after relaunch).
A folder in the app directory will be created for logs.
English:
Enable file logging (changes will take effect after relaunch).
A folder in the app directory will be created for logs.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用文件记录(更改将在游戏重新启动后生效)，
将在应用程序目录中创建一个用于记录的文件夹。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用文件記錄(更改將在遊戲重新啟動後生效)，
將在應用程序目錄中創建一個用於記錄的文件夾。
Russian:
Включить file logging (Изменения вступят в силу после перезапуска).
В директории игры будет создана папка для логов.

column1: Enable interpolation between teleports when using keybinds.
English: Enable interpolation between teleports when using keybinds.
SimplifiedChinese: 当使用按键传送时候，会使用插值模式
TraditionalChinese: 當使用按鍵傳送時候，會使用插值模式
Russian: Enable interpolation between teleports when using keybinds.

column1:
Enable teleport-through-list functionality.
Usage:
1. Put Checkmark to the teleports you want to teleport using hotkey
2. Single click the teleport (with checkmark) to select where you want to start
3. You can now press Next or Previous Hotkey to Teleport through the Checklist
Initially it will teleport the player to the selection made
Note: Double click or click the arrow to open teleport details
English:
Enable teleport-through-list functionality.
Usage:
1. Put Checkmark to the teleports you want to teleport using hotkey
2. Single click the teleport (with checkmark) to select where you want to start
3. You can now press Next or Previous Hotkey to Teleport through the Checklist
Initially it will teleport the player to the selection made
Note: Double click or click the arrow to open teleport details
SimplifiedChinese:
启用列表传送功能。
用法:
1.勾选你要传送的传送点
2.单击选择以选择你要开始的位置
3.现在可以通过传送下一个/传送上一个进行传送
会先传送到玩家选择的第一个点位。

注意:点击箭头可以打开详细信息。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用列表傳送功能。
用法:
1.勾選你要傳送的傳送點
2.單擊選擇以選擇你要開始的位置
3.現在可以通過傳送下一個/傳送上一個進行傳送
會先傳送到玩家選擇的第一個點位。

注意:點擊箭頭可以打開詳細信息。
Russian:
Включить функцию телепортации по списку.
Использование:
1. Поставьте галочку напротив телепортов, к которым вы хотите телепортироваться с помощью горячей клавиши
2. Один раз кликните по телепорту (отмеченному галочкой) чтобы выбрать, с какого вы хотите начать
3. Теперь вы можете нажать горячие клавиши Next или Previous чтобы телепортироваться по загруженному списку
Изначально функция телепортирует игрока к выбранным точкам
Примечание: Щёлкните дважды или кликните на стрелку, чтобы открыть детали о телепорте

column1:
Enable teleport-to-mark functionality.
Usage: 
	1. Open map.
	2. Hold [Teleport Key] and click with the LMB anywhere in the map.
	Done. You have been teleported to selected location.
Teleport might glitch if teleporting to an extremely high location. 
Adjust Override Height accordingly to help avoid.
English:
Enable teleport-to-mark functionality.
Usage: 
	1. Open map.
	2. Hold [Teleport Key] and click with the LMB anywhere in the map.
	Done. You have been teleported to selected location.
Teleport might glitch if teleporting to an extremely high location. 
Adjust Override Height accordingly to help avoid.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用 指定地点传送 功能。
用法:
	1.打开地图
	2.按住[传送键]然后鼠标左键点击地图任意位置
	3.你将会被传送到你选择的地方
如果传送到极高的位置，传送可能会出现问题，
应当调整高度避免该情况。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用 指定地點傳送 功能。
用法:
	1.打開地圖
	2.按住[傳送鍵]然後鼠標左鍵點擊地圖任意位置
	3.你將會被傳送到你選擇的地方
如果傳送到極高的位置，傳送可能會出現問題，
應當調整高度避免該情況。
Russian:
Включить функцию телепортации к метке.
Использование: 
	1. Открыть карту.
	2. Удердживать [Кнопку телепортации/Teleport Key] и нажмите левую кнопку мыши в любой точке карты.
	Готово. Вы были телепортированы в выбранное место.
Телепортация может дать сбой при телепортации на слишком высокие места. 
Отрегулируйте Override Height соответствующим образом, чтобы избежать этого.

column1: Enable the Use of Custom HotKeys
English: Enable the Use of Custom HotKeys

column1: Enables attack multipliers. Need to choose a mode to work.
English: Enables attack multipliers. Need to choose a mode to work.
SimplifiedChinese: 启动倍攻。需要选择一种倍攻模式。
TraditionalChinese: 啟動倍攻。需要選擇一種倍攻模式。
Russian: Включает множитель атак. Для работы нужно выбрать режим.

SimplifiedChinese: 启动自定义摄像机视距设置
TraditionalChinese: 啟動自定義攝像機變焦設置

column1:
Enables detecting gathered items.
It works only items what will be gathered after enabling this function.
Only items with blue line support this function.
English:
Enables detecting gathered items.
It works only items what will be gathered after enabling this function.
Only items with blue line support this function.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用检测收集的项目。
并且它仅适用于启用此功能后将收集的项目，
只有带有蓝线的项目支持此功能。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用檢測收集的項目。
並且它僅適用於啟用此功能後將收集的項目，
只有帶有藍線的項目支持此功能。
Russian:
Enables detecting gathered items.
It works only items what will be gathered after enabling this function.
Only items with blue line support this function.

column1: Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.
English: Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用检测不在交互式地图数据中的项目。
只有带绿线的项目支持此功能。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用檢測不在互動式地圖數據中的項目。
只有帶綠線的項目支援此功能。
Russian: Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.

column1:
Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.
Only items with green line support this function.
English:
Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.
Only items with green line support this function.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用检测不在交互式地图数据中的项目。
只有带绿线的项目支持此功能。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用檢測不在互動式地圖數據中的項目。
只有帶綠線的項目支援此功能。
Russian:
Enables detecting items what are not in interactive map data.
Only items with green line support this function.

column1:
Enables god mode when the character's health drops
below the specified minimum.
English:
Enables god mode when the character's health drops
below the specified minimum.
SimplifiedChinese:
当角色的生命值下降到
低于指定的最小值时启用无敌模式。
TraditionalChinese:
當角色的生命值下降到
低於指定的最小值時啟用無敵模式。
Russian:
Включает бессмертие, когда здоровье персонажа падает
ниже указанного минимума.

column1: Enables god mode, i.e. no incoming damage including environmental damage.
English: Enables god mode, i.e. no incoming damage including environmental damage.
SimplifiedChinese: 启用无敌模式: 不会受到伤害包括环境伤害。
TraditionalChinese: 啟用無敵模式: 不會受到傷害包括環境傷害。
Russian: Включает бессмертие, т.е. отключает весь урон персонажу, в том числе от окружающей среды.

column1: Enables kill aura. Need to choose a mode to work.
English: Enables kill aura. Need to choose a mode to work.
SimplifiedChinese: 启动杀戮光环。需要选择一个工作模式。
TraditionalChinese: 啟動殺戮光環。需要選擇一個工作模式。
Russian: Включает kill aura. Для работы нужно выбрать режим.

column1:
Enables mob vacuum.
Mobs within the specified radius will move
to a specified distance in front of the player.
English:
Enables mob vacuum.
Mobs within the specified radius will move
to a specified distance in front of the player.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用生物吸附。
指定范围内的生物将移动到玩家前方的指定距离。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用生物吸附。
指定範圍內的生物將移動到玩家前方的指定距離。
Russian:
Включает mob vacuum.
Монстры в указанном радиусе будут перемещены
перед игроком на указанное растояние.

column1:
Enables multi-animation attacks.
Do keep in mind that the character's audio will also be spammed.
English:
Enables multi-animation attacks.
Do keep in mind that the character's audio will also be spammed.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用多动画攻击。
角色的音频也会触发多重。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用多動畫攻擊。
角色的音頻也會觸發多重。
Russian:
Включает мульти-анимацию атак.
Имейте ввиду, что голос персонажа также будет умножен.

column1:
Enables multi-hit.
Multiplies your attack count.
This is not well tested, and can be detected by anticheat.
Not recommended to be used with main accounts or used with high values.
English:
Enables multi-hit.
Multiplies your attack count.
This is not well tested, and can be detected by anticheat.
Not recommended to be used with main accounts or used with high values.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用多次命中，增加你的攻击计数。
这没有经过充分测试，可以通过反作弊检测到。
不建议用在主帐户上或使用过高的数值。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用多次命中，增加你的攻擊計數。
這沒有經過充分測試，可以通過反作弊檢測到。
不建議用在主帳戶上或使用過高的數值。
Russian:
Включает multi-hit.
Умножает количество ваших атак.
Функция недостаточно хорошо протестирована, поэтому может быть обнаружена анти-читом.
Не рекомендуется использовать на основном аккаунте или использовать с высокими значениями.

column1:
Enables multi-target attacks within specified radius of target.
All valid targets around initial target will be hit based on setting.
Damage numbers will only appear on initial target but all valid targets are damaged.
If multi-hit is off and there are still multiple numbers on a single target, check the Entity Manager in the Debug section to see if there are invisible entities.
This can cause EXTREME lag and quick bans if used with multi-hit. You are warned.
English:
Enables multi-target attacks within specified radius of target.
All valid targets around initial target will be hit based on setting.
Damage numbers will only appear on initial target but all valid targets are damaged.
If multi-hit is off and there are still multiple numbers on a single target, check the Entity Manager in the Debug section to see if there are invisible entities.
This can cause EXTREME lag and quick bans if used with multi-hit. You are warned.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用普攻范围将会同时攻击指定范围内的所有敌人。
伤害数字只会出现在初始目标上，但所有范围内的目标都会收到伤害。
如果未开启倍攻但在单个目标上仍有多个伤害数字，请查看[调试]中的[实体管理器]是否存在不可见的实体。
警告: 普攻范围和倍功同时使用可能会导致巨大延迟以及快速被封禁。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用多目標攻擊將會同時攻擊指定範圍內的所有敵人。
傷害數字只會出現在初始目標上，但所有範圍內的目標都會收到傷害。
如果未開啟倍攻但在單個目標上仍有多個傷害數字，請查看[調試]中的[實體管理器]是否存在不可見的實體。
警告: 多目標攻擊和倍功同時使用可能會導致巨大延遲以及快速被封禁。
Russian:
Позволяет проводить атаки по нескольким целям в пределах заданного радиуса от цели.
Все доступные цели вокруг атакуемой цели будут поражены согласно заданным настройкам.
Нанесённый урон будет отображаться только на атакуемой цели, но получат урон все.
Если функция отключена, а над целью всё ещё отображается множество значений, проверьте Entity Manager в разделе Debug чтобы увидеть, есть ли невидимые значения.
Функция может привести к ОГРОМНЫМ зависаниями быстрым банам. Вы предупреждены.

column1:
Enables no-clip (fast speed + no collision).
To move, use WASD, Space (go up), and Shift (go down), or customize your own keys.
English:
Enables no-clip (fast speed + no collision).
To move, use WASD, Space (go up), and Shift (go down), or customize your own keys.
SimplifiedChinese:
启用自由移动(快速移动+无碰撞)。
移动: WSAD
升高: Space
降低: Shift
或者自定义按键。
TraditionalChinese:
啟用自由移動(快速移動+無碰撞)。
移動: WSAD
升高: Space
降低: Shift
或者自定義按鍵。
Russian:
Включает no-clip (высокая скорость + прохождение сквозь текстуры).
Чтобы передвигаться, используйте WASD, Space (подняться вверх), и Shift (спуститься вниз), или настройте собственные клавиши.

column1:
Enemies don't attack or use abilities against player. 
May not work with some enemies or enemy abilities.
English:
Enemies don't attack or use abilities against player. 
May not work with some enemies or enemy abilities.
SimplifiedChinese:
敌人对玩家攻击或者使用技能。
也许对某些敌人不会生效。
TraditionalChinese:
敵人對玩家攻擊或者使用技能。
也許對某些敵人不會生效。
Russian:
Враги не атакуют и не используют способности против игрока. 
Может не работать с некоторыми врагами или их способностями.

column1: Everything beside Animals and Drop Items (Plants, Books, etc).
English: Everything beside Animals and Drop Items (Plants, Books, etc).
SimplifiedChinese: 除了动物和掉落物品(植物、书籍等)之外的所有东西。
TraditionalChinese: 除了動物和掉落物品(植物、書籍等)之外的所有東西。
Russian: Всё, кроме Животных и собираемых предметов (Растений, Книг, и т.д).

SimplifiedChinese: 从自动选择对话选项中 排除 凯瑟琳/壶灵/铁匠。
TraditionalChinese: 從自動選擇對話選項中 排除 凱瑟琳/壺靈/鐵匠。

SimplifiedChinese: 排除 凯瑟琳/壶灵/铁匠
TraditionalChinese: 排除 凱瑟琳/壺靈/鐵匠

column1:
Fast Cooking if the recipe has fast cooking open. 
If fast cooking is closed, you in addition need to turn on Fast Proficiency.
English:
Fast Cooking if the recipe has fast cooking open. 
If fast cooking is closed, you in addition need to turn on Fast Proficiency.
SimplifiedChinese:
自动烹饪，如果食谱已经解锁自动烹饪。

column1:
This mode prevents sending server packets with stamina cost actions,
e.g. swim, climb, sprint, etc.
NOTE: This is may be more safe than the standard method. More testing is needed.
English:
This mode prevents sending server packets with stamina cost actions,
e.g. swim, climb, sprint, etc.
NOTE: This is may be more safe than the standard method. More testing is needed.
SimplifiedChinese:
此模式可拦截包含体力消耗动作的服务器数据包，
如: 游泳、攀爬、冲刺。
注意: 这可能比标准方法更安全，需要更多测试。
TraditionalChinese:
此模式可攔截包含體力消耗動作的伺服器封包，
如: 遊泳、攀爬、沖刺。
注意: 這可能比標準方法更安全，需要更多測試。
Russian:
Этот режим предотвращает отправку пакетов с тратой энерегии на сервер,
например: плавание, карабкание, бег, др.
ВАЖНО: это может быть безопаснее обычного режима. Требуется больше проверок.

column1:
This page following with filters for items.
Items what was activated will be appear on mini/global map. (Obviously)
Each filter have options, you can access to it by clicking RMB on filter.
Filters can be marked with colored lines,
	they indicate that filter support some features. (Hover it)
Thats all for now. Happy using ^)
English:
This page following with filters for items.
Items what was activated will be appear on mini/global map. (Obviously)
Each filter have options, you can access to it by clicking RMB on filter.
Filters can be marked with colored lines,
	they indicate that filter support some features. (Hover it)
Thats all for now. Happy using ^)
SimplifiedChinese:
此页面后跟项目过滤器，
被激活的物品将出现在迷你/全球地图上(很显然)。
每个过滤器都有选项，您可以通过右键单击过滤器上来访问它。
某些过滤器右边有彩色线条标记，
	它们意味着这些过滤器支持某些特殊功能(悬停显示)
就这些了。Happy using :)
TraditionalChinese:
此頁面後跟項目過濾器，
被激活的物品將出現在迷你/全球地圖上(很顯然)。
每個過濾器都有選項，您可以通過右鍵單擊過濾器上來訪問它。
某些過濾器右邊有彩色線條標記，
	它們意味著這些過濾器支援某些特殊功能(懸停顯示)
就這些了。Happy using :)
Russian:
This page following with filters for items.
Items what was activated will be appear on mini/global map. (Obviously)
Each filter have options, you can access to it by clicking RMB on filter.
Filters can be marked with colored lines,
	they indicate that filter support some features. (Hover it)
Thats all for now. Happy using ^)

column1:
Time Speedup Multipler 
Higher Values will lead to sync issues with servers 
and is not recommended for Laggy Internet connections.

Time Speedup Multipler 
Higher Values will lead to sync issues with servers 
and is not recommended for Laggy Internet connections.
SimplifiedChinese:
游戏时间加速倍率。
更高的倍率将导致与服务器同步问题，
不推荐在较差的网络环境下使用。
TraditionalChinese:
遊戲時間加速倍率。
更高的倍率將導致與伺服器同步問題，
不推薦在較差的網絡環境下使用。
Russian:
Ускорить время 
Большие значения могут привести к проблеме синхронизации с сервером
Не рекомендуется с использованием слабого интернета.

column1:
To display paimon, turn on the function, open the profile (esc) and close it. 
If the paimon disappeared after teleportation, do not disable the function, open and close the profile.
English:
To display paimon, turn on the function, open the profile (esc) and close it. 
If the paimon disappeared after teleportation, do not disable the function, open and close the profile.
SimplifiedChinese:
想要显示派蒙，打开该功能然后打开菜单(esc)并关闭它。
如果传送后派蒙消失了，不需要关闭该功能，重新打开和关闭菜单即可。
TraditionalChinese:
想要顯示派蒙，打開該功能然後打開菜單(esc)並關閉它。
如果傳送後派蒙消失了，不需要關閉該功能，重新打開和關閉菜單即可。
Russian:
Для отображения паймон включи функцию, открой профиль (esc) и закрой это. 
Если паймон пропадает после телепортации, не выключате функцию, затем откройте и закройте профиль.
